### Register a new user
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "full_name": "Test User",
  "email": "testuser@example.com",
  "phone_number": "+251912345678",
  "password": "TestPass123!",
  "role": "donor"
}

### Login (get token)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "testuser@example.com",
  "password": "TestPass123!"
}

### List campaigns
GET http://localhost:5000/api/campaigns

### Get campaign details (replace :id)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/campaigns/:id

### Record a share (replace :id) — public endpoint
POST http://localhost:5000/api/campaigns/:id/share
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "provider": "facebook"
}

### Copy link share (counts as share)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/campaigns/:id/share
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "provider": "copy_link"
}
